videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham sends a pass into the end zone looking for WR Tutu Atwell, but Clemson safety K'Von Wallace catches it for the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson’s Wallace secures interception in end zone) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson's Wallace secures interception in end zone

videos.description: Clemson CB Derion Kendrick bobbles the punt and it rolls into the end zone, but the Tigers are able to recover the ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson avoids disaster after muffed punt) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson avoids disaster after muffed punt

videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence attempts to throw the ball into the end zone, but Louisville DB Jack Fagot picks it off on the goal line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Louisville picks off Trevor Lawrence on the goal line) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Louisville picks off Trevor Lawrence on the goal line

videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence throws the ball into the end zone and gets intercepted by Louisville DB Russ Yeast.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence gets picked off for a second time) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence gets picked off for a second time

videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence sends a pass to the back of the end zone, and WR Joe Ngata jumps high to make the catch for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson’s Ngata makes leaping TD grab) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson's Ngata makes leaping TD grab

videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence lobs a 25-yard pass into the end zone where WR Justyn Ross shows off his hops to make the catch for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ross makes incredible TD grab for Clemson) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ross makes incredible TD grab for Clemson

videos.description: Clemson CB Andrew Booth Jr. and Louisville DB Trenell Troutman get into a scuffle during a punt, and Booth is ejected for punching Troutman on the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson’s Booth ejected for punching Louisville player) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson's Booth ejected for punching Louisville player

videos.description: Clemson RB Travis Etienne takes the handoff and breaks a tackle on his way for a 49-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Etienne breaks free for Clemson TD run) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Etienne breaks free for Clemson TD run

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence throws two early interceptions, but winds up throwing for 233 yards and three touchdowns in Clemson's win vs. Louisville.
